# COMPONENT SYSTEM RULES (FacePe)

## Global

- Every marketing **section** is a self-contained partial: `components/{section-id}.html` (or equivalent) with one root `section` node.
- **Cards** share: `rounded-card` + `shadow-card` + `p-6 md:p-8` (Figma `24px` inner padding on product cards).
- **No orphan styles:** if two sections use the same card chrome, they share one utility bundle.

## Site header

- **Height:** `h-[100px]` desktop; inner row `h-14` vertically centered.
- **Sticky:** `sticky top-0 z-50 bg-surface-0 border-b border-border-subtle` (adjust token names to match `tailwind.config.js`).
- **CTA position:** right cluster `Contact us` (text) + `Get Started` (gradient pill).
- **Mobile:** hamburger + drawer; preserve **primary CTA** in header bar when possible.

## Site footer (Home `3139:30809`)

- **Surface:** `bg-ink-950 text-white`; padding `px-gutter py-section-y-footer`.
- **Layout:** `gap-10` between main grid and legal strip; brand column uses `gap-33` between logo block and social row (Figma **33px**).
- **Typography:** column headings `font-mono text-eyebrow-mono text-footer-label uppercase`; links `text-footer-link`; tagline `text-sm leading-5 text-footer-muted`.
- **Social:** `size-9` wells + `border` `border-footer-icon-ring` + `bg-footer-icon-well`; increase to **44px** tap target (`p-1` wrapper).
- **Columns:** horizontal `gap-footer-columns` between Product / Solutions / Company / Resources groups at `lg+`.
- **Legal:** `border-t border-white/10`; copyright `text-footer-legal uppercase`; links `text-footer-legal-link gap-9 flex`.

## Section structure (order)

1. Optional **eyebrow** (`12px`, uppercase, `brand-600`, wide tracking).
2. **H2** (or H1 in hero only).
3. **Supporting** copy (`18px`, `leading-[28px]`).
4. **CTA row** (max 2 pills + optional text links).
5. **Media / grid**.

## Feature & product cards

- **Radius:** `28px` token.
- **Padding:** `24px` inner (`p-6`).
- **Top row:** `44px` icon tile + category pill (`h-6`, `px-3`, uppercase `text-[15px]`).
- **Hover:** `translate-y-[-2px]` + shadow token bump (see `animation-rules.mdc`).
- **Footer link:** â€śLearn moreâ€ť + chevron `14px` â€” use Lucide `ArrowRight` or `ChevronRight` at `w-3.5 h-3.5`.

## Stats card

- **Number:** `~44px` bold.
- **Label:** `~21px` medium/bold per token.
- **Supporting line:** `~20px` regular.
- **Dividers:** `border-t border-border-subtle` between stat rows.

## Testimonial

- Quote â†’ body â†’ **avatar row** (`48px` square, gradient allowed) â†’ name (`22px`) + title (`16px` muted).
- Pagination dashes under testimonial: decorative `aria-hidden="true"`.

## FAQ

- **Layout:** `lg:flex-row lg:gap-faq-split`; left column intro; right **`max-w-[640px]`** accordion stack `gap-5`.
- **Badge:** `bg-lilac-25 border border-lilac-200 rounded-pill` + dot `bg-brand-600 shadow-faq-dot`.
- **States:** expanded toggle = `bg-gradient-primary`; collapsed = `bg-accordion-toggle-idle`.
- **Row height (closed):** `~81px`; **open first item** in design reference.
- **Trigger:** `button` **`32px`** visual, **44px** min hit target; `aria-expanded` + `aria-controls`.

## Buttons

- **Primary:** `bg-gradient-primary` + `shadow-primary` + `h-14` + `px-5` + `gap-2.5` + `rounded-pill`.
- **Secondary (hero):** `bg-surface-0 border border-border-subtle text-ink-950 h-14 px-5 rounded-pill-secondary`.
- **Ghost text CTA (e.g. â€śChoose your pathâ€ť, â€śContact our teamâ€ť):** `rounded-pill-soft border border-border-subtle h-btn-ghost px-btn-ghost-x gap-3 text-sm font-bold text-ink-950`.
- **Icons on CTAs:** Lucide **`16px`** default on primary/secondary hero buttons.

## Pills / badges

- **Category pills:** subtle fill on white, uppercase, **`15px`** tracking normal, **bold**.
- **Do not** use pills for eyebrowsâ€”eyebrows are plain uppercase text.

